<div id="wrapper">
<div id="leftcolumn">
<div>
  <ol>
    <li><span>1.</span><p>Disect the inner workings of any site to find other domains owned by same user.  A site's source code contains invaluable information about who is managing the webiste.  This application will scan a website's source code for individual login details that are unique to a domain owner.  Find contact details about who is using any website. </p></li>
